In order to set up a cron job, do the following:

0) Make sure you have ``tweepy`` installed on your computer

1) Edit your `crontab` as a user `my_user`:
``$ crontab -u my_user -e``

2) add the following lines to that table:
0  6  *  *  * python /home/my_user/onegin/stat.py
0  7  *  *  * python /home/my_user/onegin/onegin_paste_bot.py
